  <h2>About the Project</h2>
  <p>
    Immich Wallpaper is a macOS menu bar app that fetches random photos from an
    Immich server and applies them as desktop wallpapers on a schedule.
  </p>
  <p>
    It supports source filtering (all photos, favorites, albums, and people),
    date/location overlays, landscape-only mode, and quick actions like next image
    and open current wallpaper in Immich.
  </p>

